# Build output directory for AffineScript -> WebAssembly artifacts.
#
# The GUI loads `./assets/wasm/hypatia_gui.wasm` at runtime
# (see ../../index.html). That file is a build artifact compiled
# from `../../../tea/hypatia_gui.affine` and is NOT committed —
# Scorecard's `Binary-Artifacts` check treats committed .wasm as a
# supply-chain risk because reviewers cannot audit machine code.
#
# Compile locally before running the UI:
#
#   affc build src/ui/tea/hypatia_gui.affine \
#       --target wasm32-unknown-unknown \
#       --out src/ui/public/assets/wasm/hypatia_gui.wasm
#
# CI builds it as part of the UI job; production ships the artifact
# from a signed release, never from the repo.
